-- Bank of Cyprus says raises 1 bln euros in private placement
-- 
-- Mon Jul 28, 2014 04:42PM EDT
-- None



NICOSIA, July 28 (Reuters) - The European Bank of Reconstruction and Development (EBRD) and U.S. investor Wilbur Ross are among investors participating in a 1 billion euro capital increase of Bank of Cyprus <BOC.CY>, the bank said on Monday.

The bank said the private placement was priced at 0.24 euro per share and investors from Europe, North America and Russia participated.